sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant IstioBI as Istio Sidecar<br/>(Built-in)
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant IstioHF as Istio Sidecar<br/>(HuggingFace)
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant IstioJudge as Istio Sidecar<br/>(LLM Judge)
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant MinIO as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over HF, MinIO: Flow 4: Model Artifact Download (Init)
    HF->>HFHub: Download model (optional)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, HF token
    HFHub-->>HF: Model artifacts
    HF->>MinIO: Store/load model artifacts<br/>HTTP/9000, AWS credentials
    MinIO-->>HF: Model files to /mnt/models

    Note over Orchestrator, BuiltIn: Flow 1: Built-in PII/File-type Detection
    Orchestrator->>IstioBI: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Istio mTLS
    IstioBI->>BuiltIn: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8080
    BuiltIn->>BuiltIn: Regex matching (PII)<br/>File-type validation
    BuiltIn-->>IstioBI: Detection results<br/>(spans, scores, types)
    IstioBI-->>Orchestrator: Response<br/>Istio mTLS

    Note over Orchestrator, HF: Flow 2: HuggingFace Model Detection
    Orchestrator->>IstioHF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Istio mTLS + detector_id header
    IstioHF->>HF: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
    HF->>HF: Model inference<br/>(AutoModelForSequenceClassification<br/>or GraniteForCausalLM)
    HF-->>IstioHF: Detection results<br/>(scores, classifications)
    IstioHF-->>Orchestrator: Response<br/>Istio mTLS

    Note over Orchestrator, vLLM: Flow 3: LLM Judge Evaluation
    Orchestrator->>IstioJudge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>or /api/v1/text/generation<br/>Istio mTLS + detector_id header
    IstioJudge->>Judge: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000
    Judge->>vLLM: Evaluation prompt<br/>HTTP/8080, plaintext
    vLLM-->>Judge: LLM evaluation response
    Judge-->>IstioJudge: Detection results<br/>(judge scores, metrics)
    IstioJudge-->>Orchestrator: Response<br/>Istio mTLS
